snippet: A Mississippi River barge overturned while unloading steel coils in northeast Arkansas on Tuesday, and authorities were searching for two people who fell into the water and went missing....

headline.print_headline: Barge Capsizes on Mississippi River; 2 Missing
headline.main: Barge Capsizes on Mississippi River; 2 Missing

lead_paragraph: A Mississippi River barge overturned while unloading steel coils in northeast Arkansas on Tuesday, and authorities were searching for two people who fell into the water and went missing.
